===========
whatsonpypi
===========


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/whatsonpypi.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/whatsonpypi

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/viseshrp/whatsonpypi.svg
